---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTASection from '@/components/sections/CTASection.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About Jason Petersen" description="Meet Jason Petersen, Associate Broker / Sales Agent with Bear Lake View Realty and a local Bear Lake-area guide for Utah and Idaho real estate.">
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="container-wide grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[0.95fr_1.05fr]">
      <div><img class="rounded-[2rem] border border-white shadow-soft" src="/images/placeholders/jason-headshot-placeholder.svg" alt="Professional headshot placeholder for Jason Petersen" /></div>
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">About Jason</p>
        <h1 class="mt-4 font-serif text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Local Bear Lake guidance from Jason Petersen</h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-lake-900/75">Jason Petersen is an Associate Broker / Sales Agent with Bear Lake View Realty, licensed in Utah and Idaho. With 25+ years living in the Bear Lake area, he helps clients understand local property differences that online search tools may miss.</p>
        <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
          {['25+ years in the area', 'Fast communication and follow-through', 'Utah and Idaho side insight', 'Builder connections for lot buyers'].map((item) => <div class="card"><h2 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold">{item}</h2></div>)}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="bg-white py-16">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-semibold">A practical local guide — not just another search result</h2>
      <p class="mt-5 leading-8 text-lake-900/75">Bear Lake real estate can involve second-home timing, cabin maintenance, winter access, local rental rules, building constraints, HOA expectations, lake access, and community differences between Garden City, Fish Haven, Laketown, St. Charles, and nearby areas. Jason’s role is to help you ask better questions before you make a decision.</p>
      <p class="mt-5 leading-8 text-lake-900/75">Clients value Jason’s communication style: he returns calls and texts quickly, follows through, and keeps the process conversational. For lot buyers, he can also help connect you with builders and local resources as you evaluate whether building makes sense.</p>
      <div class="mt-8 rounded-3xl border border-dashed border-lake-900/20 bg-lake-50 p-6"><h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold">Future personal/community details</h3><p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-lake-900/70">Placeholder for family, community involvement, favorite Bear Lake activities, professional background, and real photos once approved.</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <CTASection />
</BaseLayout>
